    "description": "《篝火与尾巴 bonfire and tail》是无明工作室(avidya studio)开发的一款多人游玩的派对动作游戏。 <br>我们做这款游戏的初衷是希望可以与玩家们一起回到童年的时候，暂时丢下生活的烦恼，去感受孩提时初见游戏那种原始的快乐。<br>游戏主打轻快的节奏，简洁明亮的画风，可爱的小福瑞们伴随温暖的篝火一起照亮每一名玩家年轻的心。<br>游戏包含了十余种各具特色的小游戏玩法，轻松有趣又刺激，和小伙伴们尽情玩耍吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/e3c5961212beb7423c22f48df5b15b75.poster.avif?t=1694257739\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/e3c5961212beb7423c22f48df5b15b75.webm?t=1694257739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/e3c5961212beb7423c22f48df5b15b75.mp4?t=1694257739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/5e5d1752839e389ef204bcdfc265e8e2.poster.avif?t=1694257739\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/5e5d1752839e389ef204bcdfc265e8e2.webm?t=1694257739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/5e5d1752839e389ef204bcdfc265e8e2.mp4?t=1694257739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/ce637b660bd47b3a0eeadc916d5b3bd4.poster.avif?t=1694257739\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/ce637b660bd47b3a0eeadc916d5b3bd4.webm?t=1694257739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/ce637b660bd47b3a0eeadc916d5b3bd4.mp4?t=1694257739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>无论用任何方式，只要点燃对方玩家的尾巴即可获得积分，从而步步走向胜利，被点燃的玩家只有不停的摇动尾巴才能熄灭火焰喔。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/8fffa9e34b0c6a3f9c454bab96192dee.poster.avif?t=1694257739\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/8fffa9e34b0c6a3f9c454bab96192dee.webm?t=1694257739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/8fffa9e34b0c6a3f9c454bab96192dee.mp4?t=1694257739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/8088bcb7b2f625893e852233bed3eba8.poster.avif?t=1694257739\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/8088bcb7b2f625893e852233bed3eba8.webm?t=1694257739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/8088bcb7b2f625893e852233bed3eba8.mp4?t=1694257739\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>逐步增加的游玩角色和地图设计。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/5ca92f372e4aeb4be3e3bf4423a2d415.poster.avif?t=1694257739\" width=624 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/5ca92f372e4aeb4be3e3bf4423a2d415.webm?t=1694257739\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249700/extras/5ca92f372e4aeb4be3e3bf4423a2d41